## Scope of this environment

This machine (`{{ tailscale_hostname }}`) is a personal development environment
for work on repositories under github.com/MWest2020 only.

- Personal projects, side-projects, learning, experiments → here
- Conduction / ConductionNL / client work → NOT here, use alma
- OpenWebconcept, NLnet, municipal work → NOT here, use alma

If the operator asks to work on a non-MWest2020 repository, ask
them to confirm — this is likely an environment mix-up. If
confirmed, proceed but flag it as an exception.
